URL Schema Manipulator
------------------------------------

Version: 0.1
Author: Alistair Kearney (alistair@symphony-cms.com)
Build Date: 4th Sept 2009
Requirements: Symphony 2.0.7

Provides a mechanism for changing URL params on the fly, before a page is rendered.

Note: Doesn't really do anything yet!

[INSTALLATION]

** Note: The latest version can alway be grabbed with "git clone git://github.com/symphony/url_schema_manipulator.git"

1. Upload the 'url_schema_manipulator' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it by selecting the "URL Schema Manipulator", choose Enable from the with-selected menu, then click Apply.
